khu kulandela ukuqeqeshwa kwezinyanga ezintathu kwentsha engu-24 efinyelele kowamanqamu ngonyaka odlule ngesikhathi leli dolobha liphume umkhankaso wokuhlonza ikhono entsheni. Abamodelayo kulindeleke ukuthi baqashwe ohlelweni lweDolobha Lokuthuthukisa Imfashini ukuze kubukiswe ngemisebenzi yabasiki bengqephu bakuleli. Khonamanjalo abasiki bengqephu abasafufusa bamenywa ukuba bafake izicelo zokuba yingxenye yohlelo lokuthuthukiswa kwamakhono oluzobasiza bangene kule mboni, futhi sekuqalile ukwamukelwa kwezicelo zohlelo lokweluleka abasiki bengqephu luka-2022, iDurban Fashion Fair (DFF) Mentorship Programme.